<HEADLINE> Results of Malaysian Open Badminton </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, July 13 (Xinhua) -- Following are the finals
results of the Malaysian Open badminton tournament on Sunday:
</P>
