Men's Singles:
</P>
<P>
Hermawan Susanto, Indonesia, bt Peter Gade Christensen,
Denmark, 15-11,15-11.
</P>
<P>
Men's Doubles:
</P>
<P>
Rexy Manaiky/Ricky Subagia, Indonesia, bt Ariantho
Antonius/Denny Kantono, Indonesia, 17-15, 15-12.
</P>
<P>
Women's singles:
</P>
<P>
Susi Susanti, Indonesia bt Ye Zhaoying. China, 11-5, 11-7.
</P>
<P>
Women's Doubles:
</P>
<P>
Ge Fei/Gun Jun, China, bt Liu Lu/Qiang Hong, China, 15-7,15-1.
</P>
<P>
Mixed Doubles: Liu Yong/Ge Fei, China, bt Jens Eriksen/Mariene
Thomson, Denmark, 15-12, 15-12.
</P>
