</P>
<P>
More businesses between the two countries were likely to
result from the exhibition, Economic and Commercial Councilor of
France in South Africa Marc Bouteiller said.
</P>
<P>
Bouteiller said a week ago 125 French companies were involved
in South Africa, but now the figure has increased dramatically
following the exhibition.
</P>
<P>
