<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 14 (Xinhua) -- The Hong Kong and Shanghai
Banking Corporation (HongkongBank) is introducing banknotes dated
July 1, 1997 to mark the establishment of the Hong Kong Special
Administrative Region (SAR), HongkongBank announced today.
