<HEADLINE> OPEC Oil Price Down to 17.58 Dollars a Barrel </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
VIENNA, July 14 (Xinhua) -- The average price of OPEC's basket
of seven crude oils dropped to 17.58 U.S. dollars a barrel last
week, 34 U.S. cents down from the previous week, the Vienna-based
OPEC Secretariat announced today.
</P>
<P>
The average price for June was 17.37 dollars a barrel. The
average oil price thus far this year was 19.13 dollars a barrel,
lower than its benchmark price of 21 dollars. 
