co-operative relations with China and that positive results have
been achieved in this.
</P>
<P>
He said he hopes those friendly relations will expand further
by strengthening political and trade ties.
</P>
<P>
Slatyer arrived here July 13 at the invitation of the Chinese
Ministry of Foreign Affairs.  
