<HEADLINE> Mandela, Nyerere to Attend World Youth Festival </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, July 14 (Xinhua) -- President Nelson Mandela of
South Africa and Mwalimu Julius Nyerere, former president of
Tanzania will be guests of honor at the 14th World Festival of
Youth and Students to be held in Cuba later this month.
</P>
