Srpska Republic parliament to abandon its move to unseat President
Plavsic.
</P>
<P>
Krajisnik said he cancelled his Monday trip to Sarajevo in
another attempt for meeting with Plavsic to resolve the political
crisis in the Srpska Republic. 
